    "body": "@benjthayer I agree about this \"We responsively scale the data fetch animation\", also not sure why do we need that much empty space above the animation.\r\n\r\nAnother point here is that we are fetching a lot of things, more than it's on that screenshot, but maybe we can group some items and have 4 groups to display to a user, for example everything what we're fetching may be grouped in these 4 groups:\r\n- profile (profile details and contacts belong here, cause contacts are related to the profile)\r\n- wallet (keypairs and watch only accounts belong here)\r\n- community (all communities related details)\r\n- settings (all app settings)\r\n\r\n",
